it.unibz.krdb.obda.owlrefplatform.core.queryevaluation

Class JDBCEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unibz.krdb.obda.owlrefplatform.core.queryevaluation.JDBCEngine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EvaluationEngine

    public class JDBCEngine
extends Object
implements EvaluationEngine
    The JDBC engine is a implementation of the evaluation engine interface which uses JDBC as connector to data sources. It can handle basically every data source which provides a JDBC interface.
    Author:
    Manfred Gerstgrasser
